This projet is a React+TS Web App, that helps Meta advertises draw decision tree about camapaign tuning. There will be presets of rules that consists of conditions and actions, but users can also define customized condition and action blocks and save it for later use. User can drag and drop conditions and actions from left sidebar to the canvas to build a rule tree. User can also right click on a block to remove it, copy it, add child block, copy it and all its chidren, or paste it and all its children. the rule tree will be evaluated from left to right,it is essentially if else tree. an ad might trigger one or more rules. there will be mutliple trees of rules, so there will be a management page. Users can import and export customized blocks and rules as a json file. every block on a tree will have a unique id, each tree will also have a unique id and can be named users can freely add sticky notes to the canvas to explain the rule tree. users don't have to worry about block placement, the app will automatically adjust the position of blocks to avoid overlap.